  Locus:
    Page: 42
    Verse: 10
Tags:
  - Cause & Effect
---
The one who strives for effect is always fooled more than he succeeds in
fooling others. The man and the woman of true insight can always see the
causes that prompt, the motives that underlies the acts of all with whom he
or she comes in contact.
